   <title>Maximizing Pod for Full-Screen Viewing</title>
   <conbody>
    <p><ph id="a34">To view a pod full screen:</ph></p>
    <p>Click the full-screen icon shown below and in the title bar of the pod in Figure 1-10.</p>
    <fig><title>Figure 1-10: Full-screen Pod View</title><image href="./media/Image_035.png" placement="break" scale="40"/></fig>
    <p>Press <b>ESC </b>to exit full-screen view and return to the dashboard view.</p>
